# JSBin Tipps and Tricks
Some tipps regarding the usage of [JSBin](http://jsbin.com).

## Customizing JS Bin's Editor

<iframe width="560" height="315" src="http://www.youtube.com/embed/pzFqaRJwNQ8" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>

All the editor specific settings are directly forwarded to [CodeMirror](http://codemirror.net/) which is the editor used inside JSbin. The keys can be found [here](http://codemirror.net/doc/manual.html#config) and set with

    jsbin.settings.editor.<code_mirror_key> = <value>

Another interesting setting:

    jsbin.settings.debug = true;